The '''feejay''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of small, [[Sentience/Legends|non-sentient]] creature that was recognized by its three arms and three head tentacles. Widely considered a delicacy among [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]], a broiled feejay was once poisoned by the thug [[Olag Greck]], and served to a Hutt crimelord.

When the target of the attempted poisoning failed to die, Greck blamed the feejay on the [[Indobok Pirates]], who were in the Hutt's employ, and had them all sent to work in the [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]] mines.

